    <a href="/author/shani-silver" rel="author"><span itemprop="author">Shani Silver</span></a>
    
      
      
    </p>

    <div class="body">We know you're seeing florals everywhere (link to main story), but as with any trend, you might find yourself in need of a little sartorial guidance when it comes to actually incorporating something new into your wardrobe. That's why you have us! Of all the floral fashion we've come across lately, these perfect pants are one of our favorites, and we're so enamored that we count them as an essential piece to add to your spring stock. This chic print is a snap to style, and we've assembled two looks that will get you started. Take our seasonal outfit inspiration to heart, and by the time warmer weather arrives, your printed pant styling skills will be blooming. You know the saying: April showers...<br><br><img src="//static2.refinery29.com/bin/entry/2eb/x/158452/day-slide.jpg" alt="day_slide"><br><br><strong>Zara</strong> Printed Trousers, $79.90, available at <a href="http://www.zara.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/product/us/en/zara-us-S2012/189505/706512/PRINTED%2BTROUSERS" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Zara</a>.  <strong>T. Babaton</strong> Meredith Blouse, $110, available at <a href="http://aritzia.com/fashion/tops/meredith-blouse" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Aritzia</a>.  <strong>Romwe</strong> Check Stitching Flat Shoes, $83.99, available at <a href="http://www.romwe.com/check-stitching-apricot-flat-shoes-p-27923.html" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Romwe</a>. <strong>H&amp;M</strong> Purl-Knit Sweater, $17.95, available at <a href="http://www.hm.com/us/product/97948?article=97948-B" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">H&amp;M</a>. <strong>ASOS</strong> Round Sunglasses with Metal Bridge Detail and Revo Lens, $21.49, available at <a href="http://us.asos.com/ASOS-Round-Sunglasses-with-Metal-Bridge-Detail-and-Revo-Lens/xuz5g/?iid=1894474&amp;cid=4545&amp;sh=0&amp;pge=0&amp;pgesize=200&amp;sort=-1&amp;clr=Black&amp;mporgp=L0FTT1MvQVNPUy1Sb3VuZC1TdW5nbGFzc2VzLXdpdGgtTWV0YWwtQnJpZGdlLURldGFpbC1hbmQtUmV2by1MZW5zL1Byb2Qv" rel="nofollow" target="_bla