    <h2><a href="/stylish-girls-cooper-building" class="title">Meet 13 Cooper Building Cuties Who Are Dressed To Thrill</a></h2>
    <p class="byline">

      By 
    
    <a href="/author/brenna-egan" rel="author"><span itemprop="author">Brenna Egan</span></a>,     
          Photographed by
    
    <a href="/author/molly-cranna" rel="author"><span itemprop="author">Molly Cranna</span></a>
    
      
      
    </p>

    <div class="body">If there’s one spot in town <strong>where killer style prowls behind every door</strong>, and no sartorial stone goes unturned, it's the iconic Cooper Building. This is where the real fashion happens, people. <p></p>

These sales teams are so many seasons ahead of us, and <strong>the clothing-obsessed guys and gals in each and every showroom hobnob with buyers</strong> from around the globe, on the regular. Obviously, they can’t look like schlubs while they're at it, so their dressing game is top notch. And after you peruse this set of lookers, you’ll want to emulate every showstopper in the cool downtown edifice. 
</div>

                <div class="long-asset horiz">
        <a href="/stylish-girls-cooper-building">
                      <img src="http://static3.refinery29.com/bin/entry/4b9/600x500b/157056/01.jpg" alt="01"    />
          
        </a>
        <a href="/stylish-girls-cooper-building"><div class="slideshow-ribbon lg"></div></a>
      </div>
      
    

  </div>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>
      
      
    
          
      
      
      
      

      
      
              <div id="entry-28335" class="preview">
  <div class="entry-header">
  
  
	  	<div class="category">Chicago</div>
    <div class="deliminator"></div>
	
  <div class="category"><!--<a href="/chicago/fashion/fashion-tips" data-track="entry:header:Fashion Tips">-->Fashion Tips<!--</a>--></div>
  
  <div class="deliminator"></div>
  
  <div class="date">
          Mar 2, 2012 9:05 AM CST
      <!-- <span itemprop="datePublished">2012-03-02 09:05:00 CST</span> -->
    
  </div>
  <div class="asset-info">
      <!-- Facebook Like -->
      <div class="facebook" itemprop="interactionCount">
        <fb:like layout="button_count" href="http://www.refinery29.com/outfit-for-nellcote" width="90"></fb:like>
