    <h2><a href="/hourglass-figure-styling-tips" class="title">Va-Va-Voom! 10 Pieces To Get That Hourglass Figure</a></h2>
    <p class="byline">

      By 
    
    <a href="/author/connie-wang" rel="author"><span itemprop="author">Connie Wang</span></a>,     
    
    <a href="/author/willow-lindley" rel="author"><span itemprop="author">Willow Lindley</span></a>
    
      
      
    </p>

    <div class="body">Whether your body more closely resembles a can of soda than a Coke bottle or you just want to flaunt the curves you were blessed with, we've got your backs. Now, more than ever before, that hourglass figure is the shape to celebrate. So, bring out those belts and start looking through your skirts; here's how to channel your inner vamp and give that oversized blazer a rest.</div>

                <div class="long-asset vert">
        <a href="/hourglass-figure-styling-tips">
                      <img src="http://static1.refinery29.com/bin/entry/f68/333x500b/155059/painted-on-stella-mccartney.jpg" alt="painted-on-stella-mccartney"    />
          
        </a>
        <a href="/hourglass-figure-styling-tips"><div class="slideshow-ribbon lg"></div></a>
      </div>
      
    

  </div>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>
      
      
    
          
      
      
      
      

      
      
              <div id="entry-28158" class="preview">
  <div class="entry-header">
  
  
	
  <div class="category"><!--<a href="/everywhere/fashion/fashion-tips" data-track="entry:header:Fashion Tips">-->Fashion Tips<!--</a>--></div>
  
  <div class="deliminator"></div>
  
  <div class="date">
          Feb 27, 2012 4:20 PM
      <!-- <span itemprop="datePublished">2012-02-27 16:20:00</span> -->
    
  </div>
  <div class="asset-info">
      <!-- Facebook Like -->
      <div class="facebook" itemprop="interactionCount">
        <fb:like layout="button_count" href="http://www.refinery29.com/spring-doll-dress-shape" width="90"></fb:like>
